                     <ref type="witness">II 853: 6</ref>
                  </bibl>
                  <cit type="translatio" xml:lang="de">
                     <quote>And Jacob fed the rest (notharoth) of Laban’s flocks (Gen 30,36). Resh Laqish said: Nothereth is written, implying, some of the poorest, the barren ones, and the sickly. (Freedman / Simon I 674)</quote>
